import React from 'react'; import { Row, Col, Card } from 'react-bootstrap'; export default function RestauCard(props) { return (
{localRestaurants.length && (props.localRestaurants.map(item =>
{item.restaurant.name}

{item.restaurant.cuisines}

{item.restaurant.location.address}

{item.restaurant.location.locality}

{item.restaurant.establishment[0]}

{item.restaurant.average_cost_for_two}$

{item.restaurant.user_rating.aggregate_rating}

 ))}
) }
